{"tid":1086881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係講笑 台灣人真係高大陸人幾班","createTime":"2019-04-01T04:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T05:29:03.000Z","uid":219712,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e694d9656125921087a5c03fbda815aaef7618da","tid":1086881,"uid":219712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"話説今日搭小巴去飲茶 <br />\n排隊排我後面嗰個係大陸落黎嘅阿師奶<br />\n一上車 我嘟緊八達通 佢係後面逼上黎 仲要攞住架車仔 <br />\n又唔係無位喎<br />\n你急唔緊要 逼到人又整到人呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n之後去到飲茶啦<br />\n對面嚟左對台灣人 <br />\n一坐低 就同啲姐姐講 早上好 又勁好禮貌咁 <br />\n嘢食嚟到 猛咁講 謝謝謝謝<br />\n最緊要係佢地肯講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n所以台灣人真係高大陸人幾班！"},{"pid":"15d524ca7a138ec29d1dad59fb2aae3df5030fb1","tid":1086881,"uid":69753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"d392e8f266e5ae7e875d3ca1a5c0f9b10d0bcb46","tid":1086881,"uid":24282,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"咪又係中國人😂🤙🏻"},{"pid":"459a777d69a156b46c3cdfa9d9a1638e35df81d3","tid":1086881,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"至少台灣冇文革 有良心嘅人冇死咁九成先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c079e5d4f1e7afc0b4464eea661547bd1c05ffba","tid":1086881,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d392e8f266e5ae7e875d3ca1a5c0f9b10d0bcb46","tid":1086881,"uid":24282,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"咪又係中國人😂🤙🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"f2803a7620bb36beb611fc4a931e31eca3d5f5ae","tid":1086881,"uid":225760,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e6c4ac40864917774fb7cdf71988c9509085528","tid":1086881,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"未又係支那生蕃"},{"pid":"3698177bef3768fa52d00d48f3d20d2497f5c9b4","tid":1086881,"uid"